posting_body: ['NO SPECIALS', 'Links at Westridge', '25330 Silver Aspen Way, Valencia, CA, 91381', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 71', 'OR Text', '71', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL>', 'Your New Home Awaits!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1041-1052 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to our stunning apartments in beautiful Valencia, CA – a city that has earned the title of awesometown from residents and visitors alike.', 'Simply stated, the awesome and unique lifestyle in Valencia is difficult to find anywhere else.', "You'll be within minutes of excellent schools, amazing paths and trails, as well as an awesome town center with an array of shopping, entertainment, and cultural activities.", "At Links at Westridge, you'll be in one of the most premier locations in Santa Clarita, CA surrounded by extensive nearby attractions.", "In addition, you'll have exclusive access to the collection of thoughtful amenities available just outside your door.", "Whether it's a relaxing swim in the resort class swimming pool, an intense workout at our fully equipped 24-hour fitness center, or a fun BBQ just outside the clubroom, you'll have a variety of luxuries within reach.", 'Best of all, we are located adjacent to the renowned 18-hole championship golf course, TPC at Valencia!', 'Experience the essence of comfort and style – come home to Links at Westridge today!', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet lovers UNITE!', 'Keep your pet happy at our property.', 'Restrictions apply.', 'Driving Directions:', 'Located on the Old Road in Valencia across the street from the Local Bar and Grill.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday:12:00PM-4:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'hk5ecuSdmX']
